HEADWORD: Subnect
<hw>Sub*nect"</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>v. t.</pos> <ety>[L.
<ets>subnectere</ets>, <ets>subnextum</ets>; <ets>sub</ets> under +
<ets>nectere</ets> to tie.]</ety> <def>To tie or fasten beneath; to join
